  "section_id": "38-ranovus",
  "title": "Ranovus",
  "title_translation": "拉诺维斯",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "Ranovus is focused on both optical chiplet technology as well as laser design and manufacturing. They have taped out products across a few different paths, a monolithic CPO product at GlobalFoundries and a TSMC PIC tape out.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0549",
      "parent_block_index": 549,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
