    {
      "id": "p005",
      "index": 5,
      "source": "Ranovus’ go to market is centered around providing the interoperable solutions that customers want. For now, this means 100G PAM4 DR optics, but the use of Microring Resonators for modulation enables a pivot to other schemes such as 56 Gbaud NRZ but using WDM combining 4 lambdas to deliver 400G per fiber pair.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0554",
      "parent_block_index": 554,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "Ranovus’ go to market is centered around providing the interoperable solutions that customers want. For now, this means 100G PAM4 DR optics, but the use of Microring Resonators for modulation enables a pivot to other schemes such as 56 Gbaud NRZ but using WDM combining 4 lambdas to deliver 400G per fiber pair.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "Ranovus’ go to market is centered around providing the interoperable solutions that customers want. For now, this means 100G PAM4 DR optics, but the use of Microring Resonators for modulation enables a pivot to other schemes such as 56 Gbaud NRZ but using WDM combining 4 lambdas to deliver 400G per fiber pair.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
