    {
      "id": "p006",
      "index": 6,
      "source": "Ranovus has demonstrated interoperability with AMD on its 800G chiplet and has partnered with MediaTek to offer the Odin direct-drive CPO 3.0 as a chiplet solution for future custom silicon XPUs from Hyperscalers.",
